# Per-content visibility (the thesis surface). Unmatched paths are Public.
# docs/pitch/ is the genuinely-sealed-from-agents path (ADR 0026): the
# zero-knowledge-host product notes, restricted to the dev identity.
docs/pitch/** restricted=connor
# The product site is deliberately, explicitly Public (already the default).
# Sealed content stays out of site deploys twice over: GitHub `main` is the
# sealed-free projection (the future auto-deploy input), and the interim
# manual `vercel --prod` upload is gated by .vercelignore's site-only
# allowlist (spec docs/specs/loot-site.md §1–2).
site/** public
